headline: Reflecting On Research Tools & Consumables Stocks’ Q2 Earnings: Mettler-Toledo (NYSE:MTD)
summary: As the craze of earnings season draws to a close, here’s a look back at some of the most exciting (and some less so) results from Q2. Today, we are looking at research tools & consumables stocks, starting with Mettler-Toledo (NYSE:MTD).
